replies.body:
It's perfectly understandable, everyone has knee-jerk reactions when they find something they liked got changed.

More importantly, I applaud you at being able to look at new Aatrox in an unbiased manner.

{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}

If you still hate MOST of them, that means you don't hate SOME of them.

It's working, it's just taking longer than usual. Perhaps your neuro-plasticity was damaged from too many years of playing MOBAs?


{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}
